<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7532> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7532" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Senator in 129 (MRR 2.497; Sherk, RDGE 63-73, no. 12). Being sixth in order in the list of the consilium, he was probably of praetorian rank. See Syme, Historia 5, 1956, 206-RP 2.318. On possible datings, see above, on M'. Aquillius (10).\n" .
